Mobster grabs WarMachine's kick but in blown backwards by the shots. He
grumbles about never getting any help and throws a charge (My first oen
ever) at WarMachine. A few autoguns get knocked from the base and others are
destroyed. Some pieces go flying through the air and clatter on the ground.
The autoguns fire some more. The bigger autoguns fire bigger blasts...
